    "created_at": "2012-10-01T22:28:52Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-10-01T22:28:52Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "If this is to be merged, I would recommend that the future only be applied to files where it matters, not all files with imports.  I think a massive patch that does nothing only adds a bunch of unhelpful noise, and I hope we wouldn't be recommending that every new file should start with the absolute import future, regardless of its relevance.\n"
